{"tid":436663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風去露營   10中國男女斷水斷糧被困","createTime":"2017-10-15T10:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T16:05:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6f0ac038819444a088f6e208bf8b0cfc2b4747","tid":436663,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1508053232_595a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1508053232_595a.jpg&h=9f7e98f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被困遊客獲救回西貢碼頭上岸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 【15:15】10人已安全離開橋咀島<br />\n<br />\n中午12時半許，10名內地男女在西貢橋咀島露營(兩日一夜)，因風暴關係街渡停開被困島上，眾人斷水斷糧報警求助。警方派出水警輪協助，並聯絡區內船家趕赴現場接戴被困男女。<br />\n<br />\n被困內地人分別5男5女，年齡介乎21至57歲，其中有8名較年青的來自深圳，另有兩人來自湖北，他們沒有受傷，乘搭街渡返回西貢碼頭後，再坐小巴出市區。<br />\n<br />\n其中來自湖北的女遊客稱，今次是第一次來港旅遊，昨日到橋咀島前已獲悉有風暴，但因為從未遇過颱風，所以不知道風暴的威力，亦不知道在風暴期間沒有街渡服務。有被困內地客亦稱，只帶備一天的食水到島上，求救前已斷水斷糧，因沒有方法聯絡其他船家，所以報警求助，待救期間到廁所避風雨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334802&d=RvflC8M4JOGOVo1dpxl6kBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=57ec4931\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334802&h=f8f3baaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334802</a>"},{"pid":"a8e9cb802e4ad0e55977d8bcf30c9fa18fcd963b","tid":436663,"uid":51041,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:34:30.000Z","msg":"頭先新聞影到<br />\n有條女好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1396a3ee592ab70bba2ad76091cc7bae820b59e3","tid":436663,"uid":29835,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】十名內地旅客在西貢橋咀島露營遇上颱風襲港，沒有船離開，需要報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五男五女的內地旅客</span>由水警輪送返西貢新公眾碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n中午十二時許，警方接獲一名內地旅客報警，指一行十人在西貢橋咀島露營，因街渡停航被困島上，帶來的糧水已耗盡所以報警求助，警方派出水警輪營救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費納稅人金錢<br />\n唔知五男五女去露營做咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3af838e04f17ab5cbe8396a69209bfb339648d","tid":436663,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先新聞影到<br />\n有條女好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48efd450b70a5d9ac8f43b099743e7542fb7eeb","tid":436663,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"長腿短裙好撚柒正"},{"pid":"70f56b003ef43946216d8f67055d15212f734ad5","tid":436663,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"圖圖圖啊"},{"pid":"0ecec0f00859ce9fb97f4100802d99083e4e6904","tid":436663,"uid":3167,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/183839_9c53e22f5328a7e59bbbc0983580e554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F183839_9c53e22f5328a7e59bbbc0983580e554.jpg&h=4fa06df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904b3222b599f3